{"ID":"20260609132914-n3qlaln","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609132914-n3qlaln","title":"2020年全国Ⅰ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609132928-596wbop","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132928-596wbop","updated":"20260609132928"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在中国各种艺术形式中，篆刻是一个"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的门类。篆刻是从实用印章的应用中发展而来的，中国的印章最初用在制陶工艺方面，上面镌刻的是图案、花纹或族徽，到春秋战国时期，刻有官职名或人名的文字印章得到普遍使用，唐宋以后，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"由于文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，使这门从前主要由工匠承揽的技艺，增加了人文意味"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，印章不再局限于用来昭示身份与权力，而是通过镌刻人名字号，斋馆名称、成语警句等来表达情趣志向，印章也就超越实用功能，成为文人表达自己审美追求的独特方式。中国印章艺术由此实现了一次完美的升华——演变为中国文化特有的篆刻艺术。明清时期，众多"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的艺木家在篆刻上融入了对汉字形体的研究和理解，再加上他们对印面布局的精心设计,对各种刀法的熟练掌握,篆刻艺术迅速走向成熟并孕育出"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的流派风格。篆刻艺术的发展及成就，使印章成为与中国画、中国书法紧密结合的艺术形式，同时也是中国画和书法作品中"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"的组成部分。"}]},{"ID":"20260609132914-l69uknl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132914-l69uknl","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-rfsxp2j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-rfsxp2j","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．一次填入文中横线上的词语，全部恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-aufpo7a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-aufpo7a","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．别具匠心   才思敏捷   异彩纷呈   弥足珍贵"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-7nodmdl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-7nodmdl","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．别具匠心   才华横溢   奇光异彩   不可或缺"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-ne56ggk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-ne56ggk","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．十分独特   才华横溢   异彩纷呈   不可或缺"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-mgcpbm5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-mgcpbm5","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．十分独特   才思敏捷   奇光异彩   弥足珍贵"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-mqamijl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-mqamijl","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．文中画横线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-9aeq1mk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-9aeq1mk","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．由于文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，使这门从前主要由工匠传承的技艺，增加了人文意味"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-6v7utvi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-6v7utvi","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．由于文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，这门从前主要由工匠承揽的技艺，增加了人文意味"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-25r6tmz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-25r6tmz","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，使这门从前主要由工匠承揽的技艺，增加了人文意味"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-j34aoya","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-j34aoya","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，使这门从前主要由工匠传承的技艺，增加了人文意味"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-imfensd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-imfensd","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．下列各句中的破折号，和文中破折号作用相同的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-xbf5sdg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-xbf5sdg","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．你现在没有资格和我说话——矿上已经把你开除了"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-kpwt1jv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-kpwt1jv","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．醉心阅读使我得到了回报——我的作文常常得到老师的表扬"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-ey956dg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-ey956dg","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．我看你的性情好像没有大变——鲁贵是个很不老实的人"}]},{"ID":"20260609132939-6ckorgt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132939-6ckorgt","updated":"20260609132939"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．你永远那么青翠挺拔，风吹雨打，从不改色，刀砍火烧，永不低头——这正是英雄的井冈山人的革命精神"}]},{"ID":"20260609132914-li956ca","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132914-li956ca","updated":"20260609132948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609132914-ejrrfu2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609132914-ejrrfu2","updated":"20260609132948"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．C    18．D    19．B"}]},{"ID":"20260609132914-ot8d9dy","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609132914-ot8d9dy","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-f8k3m9y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-f8k3m9y","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题考查成语运用的能力。成语的正确运用可以从如下角度考虑：①从语境角度，用逻辑关系与词语对应解题；②从词义角度，用提取语素与词义轻重解题；③从用法角度，用适用对象与感情色彩解题。另外，还要看看搭配习惯、语法功能、使用对象等。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-dfaqbzo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-dfaqbzo","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"①别具匠心：另有一种巧妙的心思（多指文学、艺术方面创造性的构思）。十分独特：强调事物独一无二、与众不同的品性。句中用于修饰“门类”，强调这种门类的独特，而非“篆刻”技艺的精巧，所以第一空应选用“十分独特”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-b1bdn83","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-b1bdn83","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"②才思敏捷：一般指人能出口成章，形容人的反应快，思维灵活，脑子很聪明。才华横溢：意思是很有才华。句中用于修饰“艺术家”，艺术家“在篆刻上融入了对汉字形体的研究和理解”，强调了艺术家的才华，而非其思维敏捷，所以第二空应选用“才华横溢”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-8tcg3kt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-8tcg3kt","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"③异彩纷呈：比喻突出的成就或表现。奇光异彩：指奇妙的光亮和色彩。句中用于修饰“流派风格”，强调流派风格的突出表现，所以第三空选用“异彩纷呈”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-pderqq8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-pderqq8","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"④不可或缺：表示非常重要，不能有一点点的缺失，不能少一点。弥足珍贵：形容十分珍贵。句中用于修饰“组成部分”，表达篆刻艺术是中国画和书法作品的重要组成部分，强调它的重要性，所以第四空选用“不可或缺”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-8wqzop3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-8wqzop3","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-0mtunm0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-0mtunm0","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题考查病句的辨析与修改能力。解答语病类题目，先抓典型的语病标志，比如两面词、判断词、并列动词，然后压缩句子，保留主干，看是否残缺、是否搭配等。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-xsh7uka","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-xsh7uka","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"画横线的句子“由于文人士大夫参与到印章的创作中，使这门从前主要由工匠承揽的技艺，增加了人文意味”中有一处明显的错误“由于……使”，因为介词误用造成主语缺失，首先排除选项A；选项B，句子简化后是“技艺，增加了意味”，主语有问题，排除B；选项C和D句式相同，此时需要考生只需甄别“承揽”和“传承”哪一个更合适一些，“承揽”指当事人一方为他方完成一定的工作，“传承”侧重于传授和继承，而句中更强调印章艺术是工匠代代相传的，所以使用“传承”更合适一些，排除C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-nvs357i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-nvs357i","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-q0gvcii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-q0gvcii","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查正确使用标点的能力。作答时，注意前后句子的关系，了解破折号常见的用法。破折号常见的作用有：解释原因，对内容进行补充说明，表示声音延长，转移话题，表示转折、递进、总结等。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-7stilty","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-7stilty","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"句中破折号后面的内容“演变为中国文化特有的篆刻艺术”是对前面内容“完美的升华”的进一步解释说明。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-g1c6zic","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-g1c6zic","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选项A“矿上已经把你开除了”是对前面“你现在没有资格和我说话”的原因进行解释；"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-rnjbhji","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-rnjbhji","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选项B“我的作文常常得到老师的表扬”是对“回报”内容的进一步解释；"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-qd1ifn6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-qd1ifn6","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选项C属于转移话题；"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-0wl7z1o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-0wl7z1o","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"选项D是对前文内容的总结。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133000-eofk1z7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133000-eofk1z7","updated":"20260609133000"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]}]}